question_id: Film apa yang memiliki durasi terlama? Sertakan judul dan durasinya.
sql_query:
SELECT
    f.title AS judul_film,
    f.length AS durasi_film
FROM
    film f
JOIN
    film_actor fa ON f.film_id = fa.film_id
JOIN
    actor a ON fa.actor_id = a.actor_id
ORDER BY
    f.length DESC
raw_response:
```sql
SELECT
    f.title AS judul_film,
    f.length AS durasi_film
FROM
    film f
JOIN
    film_actor fa ON f.film_id = fa.film_id
JOIN
    actor a ON fa.actor_id = a.actor_id
ORDER BY
    f.length DESC;
```
